# Bitburner Scripts

This repository contains my custom scripts for the game [Bitburner](https://danielyxie.github.io/bitburner/). The scripts are designed to automate server hacking and stock market trading, helping to optimize in-game progression and profits.

## Features

- Automated server hacking: discover, hack, and grow servers efficiently.
- Stock market trading bots: buy and sell stocks based on market trends.
- Modular and customizable scripts for various Bitburner tasks.

## Getting Started

1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Copy the scripts into your Bitburner game environment.
3. Run the desired scripts from the in-game terminal.

## Disclaimer

These scripts are intended for personal use within the Bitburner game. Use them responsibly and have fun automating!

---
Happy hacking!